yes virginia its december already 
in television land that means tis the season to beg your 
parents for just one more viewing of rudolph the red nosed 
reindeer while wading through an avalanche of primetime holiday 
specials 
cbs boasts the oldest and most favored holiday fare beginning 
with the venerable twas the night before christmas narrated by 
joel grey airing at 8 pm dec 8 
the animated halfhour drawn from clement moores poem was first 
broadcast in 1974 
on dec 10 cbs will rebroadcast the i love lucy christmas 
special at 830 pm lucy ricky ethel and fred will be 
colorized for portions of this years special the segment shown 
for the first time last season after being lost for 33 years 
flashes back to some classic lucy episodes including the birth 
of little ricky 
charlie brown and that poor bedraggled christmas tree trundle 
back for the 25th anniversary of a charlie brown christmas 
yes virginia snoopy and the gang first premiered in this 
yuletide special in 1965 on dec 19 at 830 pm 
charlie brown will be preceded at 8 pm by 21yearold frosty 
the snowman narrated by jimmy durante 
cbs celebrates the holidays on its series with eight special 
episodes of shows including murphy brown and the trials of 
rosie oneill in the latter the recently divorced rosie played 
by sharon gless has her yuletide spirits dampened when she learns 
her ex and his new wife are going to midnight mass at her church 
at nbc the number of holiday programs is mind boggling from 
bob hope to the chipmunks nbc christmas fare includes more than 20 
specials and series episodes 
hope travels to bermuda for a dec 15 christmas show broadcast 
at 10 pm starring dixie carter of designing women and the 
1991 rose queen alvin and the chipmunks 30th anniversary chirp 
falsetto through another christmas on dec 8 at 8 pm 
the dreamer of oz the l frank baum story airs dec 10 at 
9 pm starring john ritter and annette otoole in a twohour tv 
movie chronicling the wizard of oz authors unlikely ascent to 
fame 
holiday segments will appear on series including la law 
dec 13 quantum leap dec 14 wings dec 14 and 
midnight caller dec 21 
abc has the fewest number of christmas specials instead the 
network focused its holiday energies on making yuletide 
installments of existing series 
dolly parton takes viewers on a family reunion in the smoky 
mountains at 9 pm on dec 21 with dolly parton christmas at 
home 
teenage sensations new kids on the block have their own 
