wednesday night on shahabuddin a career lawyer and judge 
ershad has not been seen in public for nearly a week but 
longtime aides said he remained at his home and office inside a 
dhaka military base 
the opposition claimed at least 100 people were killed by 
security forces since the emergency was declared on nov 27 
ershads govenment said only six people died 
mrs zia and hasina have been agitating for ershads ouster 
