daughter of sheik mujibur rahman bangladeshs first president 
mrs zia head of the bangladesh nationalist party is the widow 
of another former president ziaur rahman both men were 
assassinated 
ershad is the countrys ninth president since it gained 
independence from pakistan in 1971 like all of his predecessors 
he was installed by military action 
