magazine to be published in the soviet union beginning in august 
1991 
the monthly which is already published in 15 languages in 39 
countries joins a growing list of american publications scrambling 
to gain a foothold in the largely untapped soviet market 
business week magazine launched a russianlanguage edition this 
past summer the ladies home journal put a 32page russianlanguage 
insert in about 10000 copies of its november issue that it sent to 
the soviet union 
