will bank the proceeds from its sales part of the money will be 
used to pay for translating producting and distributing the 
magazine 
if the test is successful trachtenberg said the company hopes 
to proceed with other publishing ventures in the soviet union 
readers digest celebrates the power of the individual it 
gives people tools to live productive daily lives those are 
universal themes he said 
